Targeted means "show my ads to people in or interested in this area."
Excluded means "do not show my ads to people in this area." You might exclude a nearby city you don''t serve, or a location where you cannot ship. To change it, use the toggle on the location pill.', 'What does the "Targeted / Excluded" toggle mean next to a location?

