For example, if you''re a mobile pet photographer in Brooklyn and Queens, you might target those boroughs or a radius that covers them. Avoid targeting the entire country if you don''t travel that far because your ads will reach people who are too far away to hire you.', 'I work from home but serve clients in their homes or offices. How should I set Location Targeting?

In that case, you should target the areas where your clients are, not your home address specifically. 

