If you pause a campaign, your ads stop showing and you stop accruing new charges. You won''t be billed your full Daily Budget on days when the campaign isn''t running. Any previous spending stays in your Google billing history, but no new clicks are charged while paused. You can resume later and pick up where you left off.', 'Budget', '{}', 62, '[0.050704688,0.0021523437,0.028750783,0.013016016,-0.051475003,-0.014760547,0.007023438,-0.00043825686,-0.008484766,0.0029000002,0.06860313,-0.023992969,0.012608203,-0.011492383,0.07635157,0.021727344,-0.102587506,-0.024400782,-0.035094533,0.03233047,0.0135484375,0.049028125,0.009300391,0.012200391,0.001709131,-0.0050098635,0.028275002,0.031696096,0.0014797364,0.009736524,0.0022401367,-0.0033333008,-0.1192625,0.0033191408,0.025578907,-0.034233596,0.0044038086,0.00088500977,0.021704689,0.017966406,-0.01818164,-0.0036533205,0.03674844,0.012494923,-0.03631797,0.033350002,0.030019533,-0.021240234,0.035071876,0.038470313,-0.01926914,0.023245314,-0.006332422,0.004519922,0.018521486,0.0028844238,0.060628127,-0.04164219,-0.010263282,-0.0174,-0.015372266,-0.015021094,0.014103516,-0.02580547,0.018929297,0.041551564,-0.039852343,0.022350391,-0.035071876,-0.0045737308,-0.03364453,-0.004338672,0.03301016,-0.021421485,-0.02314336,-0.019960158,0.04295625,0.038175784,0.025307031,0.055326562,0.026598439,-0.0008347412,-0.04596953,0.0062474613,-0.03790391,-0.009085157,-0.03149219,0.029113282,0.004063965,0.009311719,-0.02248633,0.01759258,-0.022021875,0.023585157,0.0128800785,0.034165625,0.010127344,-0.02326797,0.04193672,0.00685918,0.044700783,-0.022996094,-0.012189063,-0.0034918946,0.0031832033,-0.03167344,-0.020209376,0.051112503,0.007046094,-0.02000547,0.0010761719,0.0022429689,-0.04229922,0.043590628,0.00888125,0.020175392,-0.006213477,0.029838283,0.014466016,-0.036159378,-0.05469219,0.04302422,-0.014092188,-0.007595508,0.03382578,0.010155665,-0.009611914,-0.002710254,0.01172461,0.005137305,0.017343359,0.02241836,0.024604687,-0.05233594,-0