INSERT INTO public.document_chunks (id, document_id, question_hash, question, answer, content, section, context, "position", embedding, created_at, updated_at) VALUES (134, 5, '59f9c19eb4e9e2384cf8cc610e18962a2d71ed8cd5ff67359520c14748dbb74b', 'Will my budget and settings affect how fast I get results?', 'Yes. A small budget or very narrow schedule/location can limit how many impressions and clicks you get, which slows down how quickly you learn what''s working. 

A larger budget, well-targeted locations, and an appropriate schedule give Google more opportunities to show your ads and collect data. If results feel slow, the first things to review are:
Is my location too broad or too narrow?
Are my ads running enough hours each day?
Is my daily budget large enough to get several clicks per day in my market?', 'Will my budget and settings affect how fast I get results?

Yes. A small budget or very narrow schedule/location can limit how many impressions and clicks you get, which slows down how quickly you learn what''s working. 

